{"id": "1294311467679612988", "channel_id": "1293860297731215431", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "堆强效还不如多堆点爆伤，堆爆伤还不如多打一张牌。\n\n但不管怎么说，强效对血链希洛还挺重要的。因为她的觉醒就是以初始面板为基数115% 130% 145%这样的成长，所以基伤要足够大，才能让觉醒的收益更大。", "timestamp": "2024-10-11T14:51:41.039000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293860297731215431", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血链·希洛的抽取建议", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
